      "message": "this method is updating the value of latestMappedToscaTemplate which is kind of hidden in the detail. From code readability if should be clearer what the method is doing\nI would suggest to change to:\nprivate Map<String, Object> getNewProperties()\nand then in the calling code check if the returned map is empty",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5269,
        "name": "Michael Morris",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michael.morris@est.tech",
        "username": "MichaelMorris"
      },
      "updated": "2022-08-25 09:26:05.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
